PO231Po231sort is a BusinessClass
    owned by po
    prefix is W6546

    Patterns
        disable StaticTranslations
        implements WorkFile

    Persistent Fields
        WorkFile                is UniqueID
        WorkFileSeq             is Numeric size 12
        PthReturnNumber         is like VendorReturn
        PthCreationDate         is Date    
        PthReturnValue          is like InternationalAmount
        PthUserId               is like User   
        PthReturnFrmLoc         is like InventoryLocation
        PthCompany              is like Company   
        PthCreditRecvd          is like InternationalAmount
        PthStatus               is Numeric size 1
        PthVendor               is like Vendor
        PthPurchFrLoc           is like VendorLocation  
        PthAuthorizeDate        is Date    
        PthRmaNumber            is Alpha size up to 64
        PthContact              is like Contact
        PthPhoneNumber			is like TelephoneNumber 
        	holds pii



        PthVenClaimType         is like VendorClaimType
        PthReplaceGoods         is Boolean
        PthOvendShpDate         is Date    
        PthVendReqDate          is Date    
        PthOrigFrtCrAm          is like InternationalAmount
        PthRtvFrtCrAm           is like InternationalAmount
        PthHandlingAm           is like InternationalAmount
        PthRetPoNumber          is like PurchaseOrder
        PthRetPoCode            is like POCode   

    Sets

        InsertionOrderSet
            indexed
            no duplicates
            primary
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                WorkFileSeq

        PO231Po231sortPO231Sort1
            indexed
            duplicates
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                PthVendor
                PthReturnNumber

        PO231Po231sortPO231Sort2
            indexed
            duplicates
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                PthReturnNumber

        PO231Po231sortPO231Sort3
            indexed
            duplicates
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                PthVendor
                PthReturnNumber

        PO231Po231sortPO231Sort4
            indexed
            duplicates
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                PthReturnNumber

    Actions

        Create is a Create Action

            Field Rules
                WorkFileSeq
                    autosequence

        Delete is a Delete Action

        DeleteAll is a Set Action
            restricted

            Parameters
                WorkFileHeader is UniqueID

            Instance Selection
                where (WorkFile = WorkFileHeader)

            Local Fields
                LWorkFileHeader is a WorkFile

            Parameter Rules
                WorkFileHeader
                    required
                    LWorkFileHeader = WorkFileHeader

            Action Rules
                Instance Rules
                    invoke Delete

                Empty Set Rules
                    invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader

                Set Rules
                    Exit Rules
                        invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader
